text = "WASD / ARROW KEYS - Movement

SPACE - JUMP

Left mouse click - Shoot / PUnch

E - Swap between punch / revolver

F - Throw / Pickup Revolver

ESC - Show cursor (Left click to refocus)

TAB - Open settings in game"

